description: One-of-a-kind penthouse offers private rooftop with STUNNING views with some of the best unobstructed skyline views in all of South Boston. Numerous renovations in recent years include NEW heating system 2022, NEW roof & roof deck 2020, NEW hot water tank 2019, new windows 2024 & many more to list! Brand new 42in cabinets, new appliances & brass hardware, 10ft ceilings & wide-open kitchen/living. Rise to meet every occasion from your built-in work-from-home alcove. Have a dog? You will be in good company in this neighborhood! Short way to the beach and Dorchester Heights Monument is just across the street. Thomas Park is located in the very heart center of Southie - Close to East Broadway cafes & boutiques & walk to West Broadway restaurants & nightlife.  Unit currently has tenant with lease through 9/1/2025 that can transfer to next owner.
